quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  22,0,Allah ke naam se jo Rehman o Raheem hai
  22,1,"logo, apne rab ke ghazab se bachcho, haqeeqat yeh hai ke qayamat ka zalzala barri ( holnaak ) cheez hai"
  22,2,"jis roz tum usay dekho ge, haal yeh ho ga ke har doodh pilanay wali apne doodh peetay bachay se ghaafil ho jaye gi, har haamla ka hamal gir jaye ga, aur log tum ko madhosh nazar ayen ge, halaank woh nashay mein nah hon ge, balkay Allah ka azaab hi kuch aisa sakht hoga"
  22,3,baaz log aisay hain jo ilm ke baghair Allah ke baray mein bhsin karte hain aur har shetan sarkash ki pairwi karne lagtay hain
  22,4,halaank uss ke to naseeb hi mein yeh likha hai ke jo is ko dost banaye ga usay woh gumraah kar ke chhorey ga aur azaab Jahannum ka rasta dukhaay ga
  22,5,"logo, agar tumhe zindagi baad mout ke baray mein kuch shak hai to tumhe maloom ho ke hum ne tum ko matti se peda kya hai, phir nutfay se, phir khoon ke lothray se, phir gosht ki booti se jo shakal wali bhi hoti hai aur be shakal bhi ( yeh hum is liye bta rahay hain ) taakay tum par haqeeqat wazeh kar den hum jis ( nutfay ) ko chahtay hain aik waqt khaas taq rehmon mein tehra-ay rakhtay hain, phir tum ko aik bachay ki soorat mein nikaal laatay hain ( phir tumhe parwarish karte hain ) taakay tum apni poori jawani ko pohncho aur tum mein se koi pehlay hi wapas bulaa liya jata hai aur koi bad tareen Umar ki taraf phair diya jata hai taakay sab kuch jan-nay ke baad phir kuch nah jaane aur tum dekhte ho ke zameen sookhi pari hai, phir jahan hum ne uss par menh barsaya ke yakayak woh phubak uthi aur phool gayi aur is ne har qisam ki khush manzar nabataat uggai shuru kar di"
  22,6,"yeh sab kuch is wajah se hai ke Allah hi haq hai, aur woh mُrdon ko zindah karta hai, aur woh har cheez par Qadir hai ,"
  22,7,"aur yeh ( iss baat ki Daleel hai ) ke qayamat ki gharri aa kar rahay gi, is mein kisi shak ki gunjaish nahi, aur Allah zaroor unn logon ko uthaye ga jo qabron mein ja chuke hain"
  22,8,"baaz aur log aisay hain jo kisi ilm aur hadaayat aur roshni bakhsnay wali kitaab ke baghair, gardan akra-ay hue"
  22,9,khuda ke baray mein jhagarte hain taakay logon ko raah e khuda se bhatka den aisay shakhs ke liye duniya mein Ruswai hai aur qayamat ke roz uss ko hum aag ke azaab ka maza chkhayin ge
  22,10,yeh hai tera woh mustaqbil jo tairay apne hathon ne tairay liye tayyar kya hai warna Allah apne bundon par zulm karne wala nahi hai
  22,11,"aur logon mein koi aisa hai jo kinare par reh kar Allah ki bandagi karta hai, agar faida howa to mutmaen ho gaya aur jo koi museebat aa gayi to ulta phir gaya uss ki duniya bhi gayi aur akhirat bhi yeh hai Sarih khasara"
  22,12,phir woh Allah ko chore kar unn ko pukaarta hai jo nah uss ko nuqsaan pouncha satke hain nah faida yeh hai gumraahi ki intahaa
  22,13,woh unn ko pukaarta hai jin ka nuqsaan unn ke naffa se qareeb tar hai bad tareen hai uss ka Mooli aur bad tareen hai uss ka Rafeeq
  22,14,"( iss ke bar aks ) Allah unn logon ko jo imaan laaye aur jinhon ne naik amal kiye, yaqeenan aisijannaton mein daakhil kere ga jin ke neechay nehrein beh rahi hon gi Allah karta hai jo kuch chahta hai"
  22,15,"jo shakhs yeh gumaan rakhta ho ke Allah duniya aur akhirat mein uss ki koi madad nah kere ga ussay chahiye ke aik rassi ke zariye aasman taq poanch kar shagaaf lagaye, phir dekh le ke aaya uss ki tadbeer kisi aisi cheez ko radd kar sakti hai jo is ko nagawaar hai"
  22,16,"aisi hi khُli khُli baton ke sath hum ne is quran ko nazil kya hai, aur hadaayat Allah jisay chahta hai deta hai"
  22,17,"jo log imaan laaye, aur jo yahodi hue, aur sabai, aur nasari, aur majoos, aur jin logon ne shirk kya, un sab ke darmain Allah qayamat ke roz faisla kar day ga, har cheez Allah ki nazar mein hai"
  22,18,"kya tum dekhte nahi ho ke Allah ke agay srbsjod hain woh sab jo asmano mein hain aur jo zameen mein hain, Sooraj aur chaand aur tarre aur pahar aur darakht aur janwar aur bohat se ensaan aur bohat se woh log bhi jo azaab ke mustahiq ho chuke hain? aur jisay Allah zaleel o khawar kar day ussay phir koi azzt dainay wala nahi hai, Allah karta hai jo kuch chahta hai"
  22,19,"yeh do fareeq hain jin ke darmain apne rab ke muamlay ka jhagra hai inn mein se woh log jinhon ne kufar kya hai unn ke liye aag ke libaas katay ja chuke hain, unn ke suron par kholta howa pani dala jaye ga"
  22,20,jis se unn ki khalen hi nahi pait ke andar ke hissay taq Gul jayen ge
  22,21,aur unn ki khabar lainay ke liye lohay ke grz hon ge
  22,22,jab kabhi woh ghabra kar Jahannum se niklny ki koshish karen ge phir usi mein dhakel diye jayen ge ke chako ab julne ki saza ka maza
  22,23,( doosri taraf ) jo log imaan laaye aur jinhon ne naik amal kiye unn ko Allah aisijannaton mein daakhil kere ga jin ke neechay nehrein beh rahi hon gi wahan woh sonay ke kanganon aur motiyon se aaraasta kiye jayen ge aur un ke libaas resham ke hon ge
  22,24,un ko pakeeza baat qubool karne ki hadaayat bakhsh gayi aur inhen khuday-e Satudah sifaat ka rasta dekhaya gaya
  22,25,"jin logon ne kufar kya aur jo ( aaj ) Allah ke rastay se rok rahay hain aur uss masjid-e haraam ki ziyarat mein Maney hain jisay hum ne sab logon ke liye banaya hai, jis mein muqami bashindon aur bahar se anay walon ke haqooq barabar hain ( unn ki rawish yaqeenan saza ki mustahiq hai ) iss ( masjid-e haraam ) mein jo bhi raasti se hatt kar zulm ka tareeqa ikhtiyar kere ga usay hum dard naak azaab ka maza chkhayin ge"
  22,26,"yaad karo woh waqt jab hum ne ibrahim ke liye iss ghar ( khanah kaaba ) ki jagah tajweez ki thi ( iss hadaayat ke sath ) ke"" mere sath kisi cheez ko shareek nah karo, aur mere ghar ko tuwaf karne walon aur qiyam o ruku o سجود karne walon ke liye pak rakho"
  22,27,aur logon ko hajj ke liye azan aam day do ke woh tumahray paas har daur daraaz maqam se paidal aur avnton par sawaar ayen
  22,28,"taakay woh faiday dekhen jo yahan unn ke liye rakhay gay hain aur chand muqarrar dinon mein unn janwaron par Allah ka naam len jo uss ne inhen bakhshay hain, khud bhi khayen aur tang dast mohtaaj ko bhi den"
  22,29,"phir apna mil kuchail daur karen aur apni nazren poori karen, aur is qadeem ghar ka tuwaf karen"
  22,30,"yeh tha ( taamer kaaba ka maqsad ) aur jo koi Allah ki qaim kardah hurmaton ka ehtram kere to yeh is ke rab ke nazdeek khud isi ke liye behtar hai aur tumahray liye maweshi janwar halal kiye gay, ma siwa unn cheezon ke jo tumhe batayi ja chuki hain pas buton ki gandagi se bachcho, jhooti baton se parhaiz karo"
  22,31,"yaksu ho kar Allah ke bande bano, is ke sath kisi ko shareek nah karo aur jo koi Allah ke sath shirk kere to goya woh aasman se gir gaya, ab ya to usay parinday uchak le jayen ge ya howa uss ko aisi jagah le ja kar pheink day gi jahan uss ke cheethrhay urr jayen ge"
  22,32,"yeh hai asal maamla ( usay samajh lau ), aur jo Allah ke muqarrar kardah Shaer ka ehtram kere to yeh dilon ke taqwa se hai"
  22,33,tumhe aik waqt muqarrar taq unn ( Huda ke janwaron ) se faida uthany ka haq hai phir unn ( ke qurbaan karne ) ki jagah isi qadeem ghar ke paas hai
  22,34,"har ammt ke liye hum ne qurbani ka aik qaida muqarrar kar diya hai taakay ( uss ammt ke log ) unn janwaron par Allah ka naam len jo uss ne unn ko bakhshay hain ( inn mukhtalif tareeqon ke andar maqsad aik hi hai ) pas tumhara khuda aik hi khuda hai aur usi ke tum Mutee farmaan bano aur ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, basharat day day aajizana rawish ikhtiyar karne walon ko"
  22,35,"jin ka haal yeh hai ke Allah ka zikar suntay hain to un ke dil kanp uthte hain, jo museebat bhi unn par aati hai uss par sabr karte hain, namaz qaim karte hain, aur jo kuch rizaq hum ne unn ko diya hai uss mein se kharch karte hain"
  22,36,"aur ( qurbani ke ) avnton ko hum ne tumahray liye Shaer Allah mein shaamil kya hai, tumahray liye unn mein BHALAI hai, pas inhen khara kar ke un par Allah ka naam lau, aur jab ( qurbani ke baad ) un ki pithain zameen par tik jayen to unn mein se khud bhi khao aur unn ko bhi khilao jo Qanaat kiye baithy hain aur unn ko bhi jo apni haajat paish karen inn janwaron ko hum ne iss terhan tumahray liye maskhar kya hai taakay tum shukriya ada karo"
  22,37,"nah unn ke gosht Allah ko pahunchte hain nah khoon, magar ussay tumhara taqwa pohanchana hai uss ne un ko tumahray liye iss terhan maskhar kya hai taakay uss ki bakhsh hui hadaayat par tum uss ki tkbir karo aur ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, basharat day day naiko car logon ko"
  22,38,yaqeenan Allah mudafat karta hai unn logon ki taraf se jo imaan laaye hain yaqeenan Allah kisi khain kafir Nemat ko pasand nahi karta
  22,39,"ijazat day di gayi unn logon ko jin ke khilaaf jung ki ja rahi hai, kyunkay woh mazloom hain, aur Allah yaqeenan un ki madad par Qadir hai"
  22,40,"yeh woh log hain jo apne gharon se na-haq nikaal diye gay sirf iss qasoor par ke woh kehte thay"" hamara rab Allah hai"" agar Allah logon ko aik dosray ke zariye dafaa nah karta rahay to khanqahain aur girja aur maabad aur masjiden, jin mein Allah ka kasrat se naam liya jata hai, sab masmaar kar daali jayen Allah zaroor unn logon ki madad kere ga jo is ki madad karen ge Allah bara taaqatwar aur zabardast hai"
  22,41,"yeh woh log hain jinhein agar hum zameen mein Iqtidaar bakhsheen to woh namaz qaim karen ge, zkoh den ge, Maroof ka hukum den ge aur munkir se mana karen ge aur tamam mamlaat ka injaam car Allah ke haath mein hai"
  22,42,"ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, agar woh tumhe jutlatay hain to unn se pehlay qoum Nooh aur Aad aur smod"
  22,43,aur qoum ibrahim aur qoum loot
  22,44,"aur ahal Mudin bhi jhutla chuke hain aur moose bhijhutla-ay ja chuke hain un sab munkareen haq ko mein ne pehlay mohlat di, phir pakar liya ab dekh lau ke meri uqobat kaisi thi"
  22,45,"kitni hi khata kar bastiyan hain jin ko hum ne tabah kya hai aur aaj woh apni chaton par Ulti pari hain, kitney hi kunvey bekar aur kitney hi qasr khandhar banay hue hain"
  22,46,kya yeh log zameen mein chalay phiray nahi hain ke inn ke dil samajhney walay aur inn ke kaan sُnne walay hotay? haqeeqat yeh hai ke ankhen andhi nahi hoten magar woh dil andhay ho jatay hain jo seenon mein hain
  22,47,"yeh log azaab ke liye jaldi macha rahay hain Allah hargiz apne waday ke khilaaf nah kere ga, magar tairay rab ke haan ka aik din tumahray shumaar ke hazaar baras ke barabar howa karta hai"
  22,48,"kitni hi bastiyan hain jo zalim theen, mein ne un ko pehlay mohlat di, phir pakar liya aur sab ko wapas to mere paas hi aana hai"
  22,49,"ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, keh do ke"" logo, mein to tumahray liye sirf woh shakhs hon jo ( bura waqt anay se pehlay ) saaf saaf khabardaar kardainay wala hon"
  22,50,phir jo imaan layein ge aur naik amal karen ge unn ke liye mughfirat hai aur azzt ki rozi
  22,51,aur jo hamari ayaat ko neecha dikhaane ki koshish karen ge woh dozakh ke yaar hain
  22,52,"aur ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, tum se pehlay hum ne nah koi rasool aisa bheja hai nah nabi ( jis ke sath yeh maamla nah paish aaya ho ke ) jab uss ne tamanna ki, shetan is ki tamanna mein khlal andaaz ho gaya iss terhan jo kuch bhi shetan khlal اندازیاں karta hai Allah un ko mita deta hai aur apni ayaat ko pukhta kar deta hai, Allah Aleem hai aur hakeem"
  22,53,( woh is liye aisa honay deta hai ) taakay shetan ki daali hui kharabi ko fitnah bana day unn logon ke liye jin ke dilon ko ( nifaq ka ) rog laga howa hai aur jin ke dil khote hain haqeeqat yeh hai ke yeh zalim log inaad mein bohat daur nikal gay hain
  22,54,"aur ilm se behra mand log jaan len ke yeh haq hai tairay rab ki taraf se aur woh is par imaan le ayen aur un ke dil is ke agay jhuk jayen, yaqeenan Allah imaan laane walon ko hamesha seedha rasta dikha deta hai"
  22,55,"inkaar karne walay to is ki taraf se shak hi mein parre rahen ge yahan taq ke ya to unn par qayamat ki gharri achanak aa jaye, ya aik manhoos din ka azaab nazil ho jaye"
  22,56,"uss roz badshahi Allah ki ho gi, aur woh un ke darmain faisla kar day ga jo imaan rakhnay walay aur amal Saleh karne walay hon ge woh Nemat bharijannaton mein jayen ge"
  22,57,aur jinhon ne kufar kya ho ga aur hamari ayaat ko jhatlaya hoga unn ke liye ruswa kin azaab hoga
  22,58,"aur jin logon ne Allah ki raah mein hijrat ki, phir qatal kar diye gay ya mar gay, Allah un ko acha rizaq day ga aur yaqeenan Allah hi behtareen Razaq hai"
  22,59,woh inhen aisi jagah pohnchaye gajs se woh khush ho jayen ge be shak Allah Aleem aur Haleem hai
  22,60,"yeh to hai unn ka haal, aur jo koi badla le, waisa hi jaissa is ke sath kya gaya, aur phir is par zayad-ti bhi ki gayi ho, to Allah is ki madad zaroor kere ga Allah maaf karne wala aur dar guzar karne wala hai"
  22,61,yeh is liye ke raat se din aur din se raat nikaalte wala Allah hi hai aur woh Sami o Baseer hai
  22,62,yeh is liye ke Allah hi haq hai aur woh sab baatil hain jinhein Allah ko chore kar yeh log pukarte hain aur Allah hi baladst aur buzurag hai
  22,63,kya tum dekhte nahi ho ke Allah aasman se pani barsata hai aur is ki badolat zameen sirsabz ho jati hai? haqeeqat yeh hai ke woh lateef o khaibar hai
  22,64,usi ka hai jo kuch asmano mein hai aur jo kuch zameen mein hai be shak wohi ghanni o hammeed hai
  22,65,"kya tum dekhte nahi ho ke uss ne woh sab kuch tumahray liye maskhar kar rakha hai jo zameen mein hai, aur isi ne kashti ko qaiday ka paband banaya hai ke woh is ke hukum se samandar mein chalti hai, aur wohi aasman ko is terhan thaamay hue ke is ke azan ke baghair woh zameen par nahi gir sakta? waqea yeh hai ke Allah logon ke haq mein bara shafeeq aur Raheem hai"
  22,66,"wohi hai jis ne tumhe zindagi bakhsh hai, wohi tum ko mout deta hai aur wohi phir tum ko zindah kere ga sach yeh hai ke ensaan bara hi munkar haq hai"
  22,67,"har ummat ke liye hum ne aik tareeq ibadat muqarrar kya hai jis ki woh pairwi karti hai, pas ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, woh iss maamla mein tum se jhagra nah karen tum apne rab ki taraf dawat do, yaqeenan tum seedhay rastay par ho"
  22,68,"aur agar woh tum se jhagrain to keh do ke"" jo kuch tum kar rahay ho Allah ko khoob maloom hai"
  22,69,"Allah qayamat ke roz tumahray darmain un sab baton ka faisla kar day ga jin mein tum ikhtilaaf karte rahay ho """
  22,70,kya tum nahi jantay ke aasman o zameen ki har cheez Allah ke ilm mein hai? sab kuch aik kitaab mein darj hai Allah ke liye yeh kuch bhi mushkil nahi hai
  22,71,yeh log Allah ko chore kar un ki ibadat kar rahay hain jin ke liye nah to is ne koi sanad nazil ki hai aur nah yeh khud unn ke baray mein koi ilm rakhtay hain inn zaalmon ke liye koi madadgaar nahi hai
  22,72,"aur jab un ko hamari saaf saaf ayaat sunai jati hain to tum dekhte ho ke munkareen haq ke chehray bighrnay lagtay hain aur aisa mahsoos hota hai ke abhi woh unn logon par toot parrin ge jo inhen hamari ayaat sunaate hain un se kaho"" mein batau tumhe ke is se badter cheez kya hai? aag, Allah ne usi ka wada unn logon ke haq mein kar rakha hai jo qubool haq se inkaar karen, aur woh bohat hi bura thikana hai """
  22,73,"logo, aik misaal di jati hai, ghhor se suno jin mabodon ko tum khuda ko chore kar pukarte ho woh sab mil kar aik makhi bhi peda karna chahain to nahi kar satke balkay agar makhi un se koi cheez chean le jaye to woh usay churra bhi nahi satke madad chahanay walay bhi kamzor aur jin se madad chahi jati hai woh bhi kamzor"
  22,74,inn logon ne Allah ki qader hi nah pehchani jaissa ke is ke pehchanney ka haq hai waqea yeh hai ke qowat aur izzat wala to Allah hi hai
  22,75,haqeeqat yeh hai ke Allah ( apne Faramin ki tarseel ke liye ) mulaika mein se bhi pegham rasan muntakhib karta hai aur insanon mein se bhi woh Sami aur Baseer hai
  22,76,"jo kuch unn ke samnay hai ussay bhi woh jaanta hai aur jo kuch unn se oojhal hai is se bhi woh waaqif hai, aur saaray mamlaat isi ki taraf rujoo hotay hain"
  22,77,"ae logo jo imaan laaye ho, ruku aur sajda karo, apne rab ki bandagi karo, aur naik kaam karo, shayad ke tum ko Falah naseeb ho"
  22,78,"Allah ki raah mein jehaad karo jaissa ke jehaad karne ka haq hai uss ne tumhe apne kaam ke liye chunn liya hai aur deen mein tum par koi tangi nahi rakhi qaim ho jao apne baap ibrahim ki millat par Allah ne pehlay bhi tumhara naam"" muslim"" rakha tha aur iss ( quran ) mein bhi ( tumhara yahi naam hai ) taakay rasool tum par gawah ho aur tum logon par gawah pas namaz qaim karo, zkoh do aur Allah se wabsta ho jao woh hai tumhara Mooli, bohat hi acha hai woh Mooli aur bohat hi acha hai woh madadgaar"
